Jangan khawatir, Bos.

427
00:20:04,900 --> 00:20:06,040
Kita pasti bisa.

428
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:08,500
Siapa bilang aku khawatir?

429
00:20:08,520 --> 00:20:09,760
Saya tidak.

430
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:12,200
Sampai jumpa besok pagi, Saitharn.

431
00:20:12,230 --> 00:20:13,400
Kita harus pergi sekarang.

432
00:20:18,120 --> 00:20:19,400
Hati-hati, nanti tumpah.

433
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:34,240
Terima kasih sudah mengantarku pulang.

434
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:37,140
Tidak masalah, Bu Mueanphae.

435
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,560
Omong-omong,

436
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:43,080
Sepertinya ada banyak penjaga di sini.

437
00:20:43,720 --> 00:20:44,560
Oh.

438
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:45,840
Ayahku berkata bahwa

439
